latestIgtvVideos.title: Aglio Olio.. 🍝
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ingredients:

Whole wheat spaghetti 
Crushed Garlic(as the name suggests lots and lots of it)
Chopped Mushrooms 
Sliced Roasted tomatoes 
Roasted Parsley powder
Parmesan cheese
Extra Virgin Olive Oil(the more the better)
Salt 
Black Pepper 
Chilli Flakes
.
. •Sauté Garlic and Mushrooms separately •Roast sliced tomatoes on a griddle
•Cook Spaghetti in boiling water with salt and oil until al dente

Now in a huge pan combine spaghetti, garlic, mushrooms, salt, pepper,chilli flakes, parsley and some extra virgin olive oil together..
Plate it and top it with some Parmesan cheese and roasted tomatoes and enjoy!!🤩 #recipes #aglioolio #newfoundhobby #cooking #foodporn #instagram #foodcoma #italianfood

latestIgtvVideos.title: Overnight Chocolate Chia Pudding 🤩
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ingredients:

Chia seeds
Oats 
Cocoa Powder
Milk of your choice(I have used almond milk)
Honey
Chopped Almonds 
Chocolate syrup 
Fruit of your choice (I have used Apples)
Sugar(Optional)
I like it without sugar!!😁 .
